First screen: 
Bubble Tea Generator
Show list of everyone's boba (fetch )
button 1: create new boba 

Second screen(after clicking button 1):
Bubble tea form with (form)
Name 
Flavor 
Ingredients list (6 ingredients and a input box for user to type in what they want)
